The reply codes currently used have the following meanings:

100 OK
101 More input required					      (for put request)
102 Request continued on next line		     (line terminated with &\n)
103 Password required						  (after login)
105 Connect							 (magic cookie)
106 Message	   (server intermittent message before ListProcessor(tm) reply)
107 Input Ready			 (server ready for client input -- proprietary)
110 Write to file							(ascii)
120 Write to file						       (binary)
130 Append to file							(ascii)
140 Append to file						       (binary)
